  "monologue": "Brief CBT-inspired reasoning: you show moderate plan-following and handle urges with micro-steps. A small disruption (urge labeling + sensory grounding) helps break automatic snacking, leveraging structure to nudge you toward deliberate choices and progress toward your target.",
